To change the mac address follow the command below =>

ifconfig wlx1cbfce04e4dd down
ifconfig wlx1cbfce04e4dd hw ether 00:11:22:33:44:55
ifconfig wlx1cbfce04e4dd down

valid mac address
>it should only contain 0-9 and a-f as it is hexa-decimal
>first pair should be 00 to avoid errors

some mac addresses =>

    00:12:34:56:67:89
    D8:32:E3:00:98:11
    


